hopobject.body:
The Deck is an Ubuntu-based penetration testing and forensics Linux distribution designed to run on the BeagleBoard-xM and BeagleBone. It has every tool you will likely need and more and is great for penetration testing on the go and for drop boxes. A complete system easily fits in a child's lunch box.

Phil also has an associated book called Hacking and Penetration Testing with Low Power Devices.
hopobject.shortdesc: The Deck is a full featured penetration testing and forensics Linux distro based on Ubuntu. It runs on the BeagleBoard-xM and BeagleBone. There is a related book as well called "Hacking and Penetration Testing with Low Power Devices".
